    {
      "id": "df443774-c13b-41c4-b545-9f0f4834638c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Many learning analytics applications for students at risk now show information to students, which may be even more discouraging for students who receive a notification that they are at risk. Authors use the platform elements of success to show students how they are progressing on a weekly basis. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
